Package com.secres

Class Main

java.lang.Object
com.secres.Main
public class Main
extends Object
Main is the main class for the application.

This class serves as the Controller, first initializing the splash screen and then notifying GraphCharts to update the ChartPanel of each JFreeChart.

The code also sets System and UIManager properties.
As the Controller class, Main creates the Models and View

Author:
Pranav Amarnath
